 I brought some things with me today

7
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:11,440
 that I want to show and tell you guys about.

8
00:00:11,440 --> 00:00:14,020
 There are two specific things, okay?

9
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:17,740
 These two things are pretty important to me.

10
00:00:17,740 --> 00:00:21,800
 They've shaped the way that I see life, myself, God.

11
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:23,400
 They've been with me for a long time.

12
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:24,340
 Well, one of them is new.

13
00:00:24,340 --> 00:00:26,700
 The other's been with me for a very long time.

14
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:30,000
 But they've really impacted my perspective.

15
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:34,200
 These two things are surrounded by two stories,

16
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:37,720
 two very distinct contexts and situations

17
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:40,900
 in which these two things will find their meaning.

18
