00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:45,060
 while putting our faith in lesser gods,

604
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:46,780
 even the good things around us,

605
00:26:46,780 --> 00:26:50,340
 placing and building our faith on that.

606
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:52,740
 Worshiping creation,

607
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:54,480
 worshiping the things that God has given us

