00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,960
 is holistic.

612
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,000
 It's gotta be both.

613
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:08,880
 It's gotta be both what we say and what we do.

614
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:11,200
 Worship with our heart and our soul.

615
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:13,800
 Yes, our words, our minds, our strength,

616
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:15,000
 with how we live.

