00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:34,840
 It's a ticking time bomb

624
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:37,440
 because the reality is the hope that it's meant for us

625
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:40,200
 to put in our faith, that we're meant to put in God,

