00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:59,820
 may you strengthen the areas that are weak.

786
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:03,700
 God, for those of us who just need to know

787
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:06,820
 of the other testimonies, will you loosen our lips, God?

788
00:35:08,580 --> 00:35:12,100
 May we be a people that speak, that sing of your goodness,

789
00:35:12,100 --> 00:35:15,320
 that tell of your goodness, may it inspire one another,

790
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:17,120
 may others be filled with hope,

791
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:19,620
 hearing about a God that's still active,

792
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:20,780
 a God that's still working.

793
00:35:20,780 --> 00:35:23,420
 God, we're not stuck in the past three years, God,

794
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:25,580
 we declare that new things are coming for this city.

795
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:27,740
 We declare that new things are coming for your people,

796
00:35:27,740 --> 00:35:29,380
 and you're going to lead us forward,

797
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:31,080
 that you will still be our God,

798
00:35:31,080 --> 00:35:32,420
 no matter what obstacles come,

799
00:35:32,420 --> 00:35:35,380
 and life can be good because you are good

800
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:37,100
 and you are with us.

801
00:35:37,100 --> 00:35:39,060
 So God, show us how to hold on to that.

802
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:43,100
 Show us how to hold on to you as we walk forward,

803
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:45,780
 as we shift our worship, as we shift our words,

804
00:35:45,780 --> 00:35:48,500
 and as we place our trust in you daily,

805
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:50,500
 will you be glorified in our lives,

806
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:54,540
 and may we see the new that you have for us.

807
00:35:54,540 --> 00:35:56,760
 It's in Jesus' name, amen.

808
00:35:56,760 --> 00:36:06,760
 [BLANK_AUDIO]

